V38.4
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The way the localization was handler could dereference invalid
     memory pointers.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Renamed the "Label" macro from the assembly support to "xLabel"
     to avoid clashes with the exec/types.i "LABEL" macro. Also the
     "WindowOpen" macro has been renamed to "xWindowOpen".

   @{b}*@{ub} Released as 1.1b.


@EndNode

