V38.6
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} The window class now makes a private copy of the NewMenu array passed via
     the WINDOW_MenuStrip attribute. Suggested by Janne Jalkanen.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: String class objects, when located in a tab-cycle order, sent
     two or even three messages to the windowclass event handler. Bug found by
     several people.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Yet another dangerous bug found in the library task-tracking
     code. Sometimes the semaphore did not get released. Bug found by Zachary
     A. Forsyth.


@EndNode

