V39.1
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the STRINGA_MinCharsVisible tag which allows you to determine how
     many characters must always remain visible in a string/integer object.
     Suggested by Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the BT_Inhibit attribute publically available. It can be used to
     determine wether or not an object is located on an invisible page.
     Suggested by Kai Szymanski.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The WINDOW_Screen attribute opened the windows as visitors on
     the specified screen.  Bug found by Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the WINDOW_PubScreen attribute as an alternative way to open
     windows on a public screen.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the WINDOW_CloseOnEsc attribute which allows the application to
     receive a WMHI_CLOSEWINDOW when the ESC key is pressed. Suggested by
     Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the VIT_Pen and VIT_DriPen attributes settable on button objects
     with a vector image.  Suggested by Nick Christie.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the LVM_REPLACE method.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the LISTV_SelectMulti attribute to multi-select listview entries.
     Suggested by Johan Eliasson.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the LISTV_SelectNotVisible and LISTV_SelectMultiNotVisible
     attributes to (multi) select entries without them being moved into the
     view area. Suggested by Johan Eliasson.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the LISTV_MultiSelectNoShift attribute to enable
     multi-(de)selections without having to use the SHIFT key. Suggested by
     Johan Eliasson.

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the LISTV_MultiSelect attribute settable with OM_SET and OM_UPDATE.
     Suggested by Kai Szymanski.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the ReplaceEntry() macro to the bgui_macros.[h|e|i] files.


@EndNode

@Node "V39.2" "changes.guide/V39.2"
@Next "V39.3"
@Prev "V39.1"
@Toc "Main"

V39.2
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} It is now possible to double-click items in a multi-selection listview
     without de-selecting the entry.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The LVM_REPLACE method did not free up the entry to replace.
     Ooops.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the LISTV_Select_All magic number for the LISTV_SelectMulti and the
     LISTV_SelectMultiNotVisible attributes. This will enable you to select
     all entries.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the LISTV_DeSelect attribute to deselect listview entries. A value
     of ~0 (-1) will deselect all entries in the list.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The BREQF_NO_PATTERN flag did not work.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the WINDOW_Borderless, WINDOW_Backdrop and WINDOW_ShowTitle
     attributes. Suggested by several people.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the following tags: FRM_BackPen, FRM_BackDriPen,
     FRM_SelectedBackPen, FRM_SelectedBackDriPen, LAB_Pen, LAB_DriPen,
     LAB_SelectedPen, LAB_SelectedDriPen. These tags are used to set the
     (dri)pens of the color of background of frames and of labels. These tags
     have been made settable with the baseclass so it is possible to change
     colors on the fly. Can't remember who suggested this.


@EndNode

