V39.4
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The stringclass object could be made active when disabled by
     ActivateGadget(). Should not happen anymore. Bug found by Florian
     Vorberger.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The previous propclass optimizations introduced a bug which
     caused clicking in the prop but not on the knob not to notify a change.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Added a work-arround for the listview->italics problem. Bug
     found by Nick Christie.


