V39.5
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} Tweaked the minimum size of the string object. Suggested by Kay Szymanski.

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the SLIDER_Min and SLIDER_Max attributes settable. Suggested by Nick
     Christie.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the STRINGA_IntegerMin and STRINGA_IntegerMax attributes. Also
     added the SM_FORMAT_STRING method. Suggested by Michael Barsoom.

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the BUTTON_Image and BUTTON_SelectedImage settable. Suggested by
     Nick Christie.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Frames do work with indicatorclass objects now. Bug found by
     Nick Christie.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Finally all problem with the string/integer objects and
     tab-cycling should be fixed now. Bug found by just about everybody.


