V39.6
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The WM_MENUDISABLED method from the windowclass did not work on
     items and subitems.  Now it does. Bug found by Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the BUTTON_EncloseImage attribute. Suggested by Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the WM_GET_SIGNAL_WINDOW method to determine the window from which
     the signal originated.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added a NULL LISTV_Entry notification when the LVM_CLEAR method is
     invoked. Suggested by Michael Barsoom.

   @{b}*@{ub} Optimized the baseclass a bit resulting in a slight general speedup.

   @{b}*@{ub} The STRINGA_TextVal/LongVal did not get notified to any target objects.
     Bug found by Janne Jalkanen.

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the BT_TextAttr attribute gettable with OM_GET.

   @{b}*@{ub} Added the WINDOW_ActNext and WINDOW_ActPrev attributes. These are only
     useful and of interest to custom BGUI class writers.

   @{b}*@{ub} The infoclass now makes a private copy of the format string. Suggested by
     Greg Patterson.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Fixed a small baseclass bug which caused mis-layouting when the
     font changed. Bug found by Nick Christie.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The infoclass did not cut of the lines properly when they went
     out of the bounds. Bug found by Daniel van Gerpen.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The Left-Amiga+V/Left-Amiga+B shortcuts in BGUI_Request() where
     mixed up. Bug found by Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} BT_TextAttr can now be set at create time which makes it possible to have
     a multifont display.

   @{b}*@{ub} Finally got rid of the anoying mouse-blocking which occured on window
     sizing and opening. Still have to get rid of it when switching pages
     though.


@EndNode

@Node "V39.7" "changes.guide/V39.7"
