V39.8
*****

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: LVM_CLEAR did not clear the LISTV_LastClicked(num) attributes.
     Bug found by Emmanuel Doguet.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: Fixed a problem with hotkeys not being disabled on page members
     which are located on a page which in turn is located on another page. Bug
     found by Joerg.

   @{b}*@{ub} BUG FIX: The cycleclass still screwed up the display when the active
     antry was changed while the object was located on an invisible page. Bug
     found by Joerg.

